The paper discusses the development of artificial general intelligence and the potential for it to become hostile to humans, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also focuses on containment strategies, which involves cybersecurity (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The ontology construction and diagramming involve cyber science (cs.CY) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
